data.description: Ideal for a first-time homebuyer or a savvy investor, don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath 1/2 duplex. Boasting a brand-new roof, recently renovated kitchen and bathrooms with new toilets, fresh carpet, and brand new exterior paint job and interior paint job only a year old, this residence is move-in ready. The corner lot property also includes a new screen for the rear patio and a convenient backyard shed.    Step inside to discover a spacious kitchen/great room combo featuring vaulted ceilings and an open floor plan, creating a welcoming and airy atmosphere with abundant natural light. The delightful Florida room opens up to a fenced backyard, providing the perfect setting to relish the beautiful Florida weather.    For those interested in an assumable mortgage, the seller's current FHA loan boasts an attractive 3.4% rate, subject to buyer qualification. Conveniently located in the sought-after East Orlando area near Chickasaw, this home offers easy access to major highways for a quick commute to downtown Orlando, theme parks, and beaches. Plus, it's just minutes away from the Orlando International Airport, with shopping plazas in close proximity.    Act now and schedule your showing today! This property is an excellent opportunity for a handy homeowner who can add their personal touch and turn it into their dream home.
